Tsssh.... I sit here writing in this digital journal that one day will no longer exist... And I wonder...

What is goin on in this world around me? What are my friends and family doin?

How is my mom doing at the hospital?
How is my dad handling it at the hospital with my mom?
Is Jas still working at the ridiculously confusing puzzle with her Sis, and Phil?
What music are Travis and Ross working on at this time of night?
Is Nicki still enjoying her party for graduation?
Did Des' finally get through her stomach pain and fall asleep peacefully? Will she be coming home soon?

I guess I'll have to wait and see... But I feel so un-accomplished, already a month of summer gone by and I haven't accomphlished shit! I have so many goals, but even more lack of motivation... For every one thought of happiness I feel ten thoughts of unhappiness trail it... 

I think in the next week I should try and accomplish something...

Well tommorow is my surgery... Number 72, and its a big one, becuase its like 5 procedures all in one operation. I am so nervous, its one surgery that can go either way... But I will just go through with it, might as well, its all for the better...
One good thing is that I asked Jasmine to go with me to keep me company and hang out with me before I go in, and after I come out... Which is kool because I won't be all nervous knowing Jas is there to keep me from going all nuts... She hasnt ever been to a hospital, or had a surgery so now she can see what its like... I am so glad she agreed to go, and that her mom said it was ok... Yay!! Maybe it wont be so bad after all... I can only pray...

            Sincerely, Tommy aka: Forlornn Angel



PS: If worse comes to worse, I shall not say whay, but, I love you all and I hoppe you know it, but don't worry, "I'll Be BacK"

Soo today I go to the ENT doctor, he checks my ears, was all great fun. 
  Then he tells me he wants to see my vocal chords, so I am like, GREAT! -_-
He decides to numb my right nostril... It was this icky blue shit... After like ten minutes of waiting he takes me into a room, and pulls out a 12 inch telescope, tells me to sit, and shows the blitch up my nose and down my throat!! EW!! I felt it go down my throat... NASTY!! Then afterwards durin the day, my nosed itched, and I picked it... and got BLUE BOOGERS!! I was like, WTF?? I showed my mom and she was like, O.o?? What the hell is that?? So yeah, I had blue boogers!! Aint ya all jealous?? GOOD BYE!!

          ~~Forlornn

Yesterday was very boring... Indeed it was, UNTIL!! Around 7:30 Sarah come on AIM, and I was like, "Wanna go to Starbucks??" I expected a no, or a I couldn't, but she could!! So after I battle my parents, we met up at Starbucks!! It was such GREAT FUN!! We talked, we laughed, we DIDN't ARGUE!! I totally was happy cuz I hadn't seed her in like a week, cuz she had been sick, but now she is all better!! Yay!! We had fun conversations. I enjoyed them, there was lots of laughing, and we shared early childhood memories, so we got to know more about each other!! It was fun, it made my week. 

  Today was kool, no skool, but I had to go to work, which was not kool!! Stupid dude there thinks cuz he is older he is in charge... FUCK HIM AND HIS BULLSHIT!! I ditched him right in the middle of something, he had to finish it on his own!! Hahahaha!! Anyways, after work I went to the normal lunch spot, it was fun for like 20 minutes. I was glad to see everyone. Megan was all hyper and stuff, and like she gave me some crappy hug, then when she was leavin, ashe spaced out while I waited for like 5 minutes for a good-bye hug, when she turned around and gave me a HUGE HUG!! We were laughin and shizz... I liked it, it was a very warm and love felt hug!! 
  My dad came home and I got a ride to the gym, that was fun, now I am all sore, my shower didnt help, and for some reason I got a beanie on.. EH, its comfy, so I dont care... I talked to Melissa today, she was all happy cuz of her BF Alon, becuz he has some suprise for her and she is all happy, I am glad she found happiness, she deserves it, she's the best person... 

  DESIREE!! I MISS YOU!! MUCH LOVE!!

  So now I am off to chat and such, talk to you all later!! Much Love!!

     ~~Forlornn


REMINDER: Surgery on the 23rd, I'd appreciate any visits on the 24th or the 25th...
